Takens embedding: delayed-time embedding technique
given a time series X(t), one can extract a sequence of vectors of the form X_i := [(X(t_i)), X(t_i + 2 tau), ..., X(t_i + M tau)]
t_i - t_i-1 := *stride*
optimisation of M and tau ?
Optimal embedding time delay based on mutual information:  3
Optimal embedding dimension based on false nearest neighbors:  10

false nearest neighbor algorithm

